; Coverage for xact.cc (auto_xact post_amount from expression)
; When an auto transaction posting uses an expression instead of a literal
; amount, the result may be a long integer or an amount.

= Expenses:Food
    (Budget:Food)    (2 * 3)

= Expenses:Rent
    (Budget:Rent)    (amount * 2)

2024/01/01 Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2024/01/02 Landlord
    Expenses:Rent    $500.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg Budget
24-Jan-01 Grocery               (Budget:Food)                $60.00       $60.00
24-Jan-02 Landlord              (Budget:Rent)              $1000.00     $1060.00
end test
